'''"Dirtbug"''' was the term used to describe investigative staff in the [[Internal Affairs/Legends|Internal Affairs]] branch of the [[Imperial Security Bureau/Legends|Imperial Security Bureau]] who were assigned to review all data collected by the field agents known as "[[Keyn (agent)|keyns]]."

